### 3Y004-230011-All Terrain Vehicles

**Solicitation Number:** WS3790553683

**Publication Date:** January 25, 2023

**Tender Closing Date:** March 9, 2023, at 2:00 pm EST

**Expected Contract Start Date:** March 13, 2023

**Expected Contract End Date:** December 31, 2023

**Notice Type:** Request for Proposal

**Procurement Category:** Goods and Services (GD)

**Trade Agreements:** This bid adheres to the following trade agreements:

* Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
* Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
* Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
* Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
* Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)
* Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA)
* North American Free Trade Agreement (NAFTA)
* Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
* Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA)
* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)

**Goods/Services Description:** Polar Knowledge Canada (POLAR) seeks the supply of eighteen (18) all-terrain vehicles (ATV) of various models, as listed in Annex A, for the Canadian High Arctic Research Station.

**Regions of Delivery:** Canada, specifically the Nunavut Territory

**Procurement Method:** Competitive – Open Bidding

**Selection Criteria:** The lowest price

**Contracting Entity:** Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)

**Contact Information:**
* Onwuama Ezechinedu, Nkechi, at nkechi.onwuamaezechinedu@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca
* (613) [insert phone number, if available]
* http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/15228035?extsite=MTUyMjgwMzVfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg== (for complete details)
